{"results":[{"aya":"050","id":4020,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"永久的乐园，园门是为他们常开的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"051","id":4021,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"他们在园中，靠在床上；他们在园中叫人拿种种水果和饮料来。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"052","id":4022,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"他们有不视非礼的、同年的伴侣。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"053","id":4023,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"这是应许你们在清算日之后得享受的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"054","id":4024,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"这确是我的给养，它将永不罄尽。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"055","id":4025,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"这是事实。放荡者必定要得一个最恶的归宿--","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"056","id":4026,"locale":"zh","sura":"038","text":"那就是火狱，他们将入其中。那卧褥真恶劣！","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":13,"previousPage":"/zh/s038-7.json","nextPage":"/zh/s038-9.json"}}